name: RedHotBIM
contents: RHB Search.MinMaxOnCurve - Search Min Max Point on a Curve, RHB Search.MinMaxOnSurface - Search Min Max Point on a Surface, RHB BoundingBox.Show - Shows the BoundingBox, RHB Point.SortByAngle - Sorts Points by Angle, RHB Vector.AngleBetween - Angle Between Two Vectors, RHB Vector.Bisector - Normalized Vector of Angle Bisector, RHB Vector.Show - Show Vector
